      dan seteru

Core

    Global Component
        ButtonWidget: The "Add to Cart" button and others can be a reusable component.
        ColorSelector: The color selection UI component.
        SizeSelector: The size picker (e.g., XS, S, M, etc.).
        ProductListTile: For the "You May Also Like" section.
    Config
        main_app.dart: Entry point of the app, responsible for navigation and initialization.
    Utils
        route_utils.dart: Handles app navigation (e.g., opening product details or the store locator).
    Constants
        Strings: Product titles, button texts, and section headers like "You May Also Like."
        Colors: Theme colors (black for buttons, white background, etc.).
        Images: Paths for images like product previews.

Data

    Model
        ProductModel: Represents a product with attributes like name, price, color options, size, etc.
    Dummy
        DummyProductData: Contains placeholder data for products in the "You May Also Like" section.

Features

    ProductDetail
        Screen
            ProductDetailScreen.dart: Main screen for the product detail view.
        Widgets
            AddToCartButton.dart: Manages the "Add to Cart" functionality.
            ColorPicker.dart: UI for selecting colors.
            SizeSelector.dart: UI for selecting sizes.
            YouMayAlsoLikeGrid.dart: Displays related products.
        Controller
            ProductDetailController.dart: Handles business logic for the product detail page, like updating the cart or fetching related products.

    StoreLocator
        Screen
            StoreLocatorScreen.dart: Screen for finding stores.
        Widgets
            MapView.dart: Displays the map for store locations.
            StoreListItem.dart: A reusable widget for displaying individual store details.

    Cart
        Screen
            CartScreen.dart: Displays products added to the cart.
        Widgets
            CartItemTile.dart: Displays each product in the cart.

